The message is not the same order;

```jsx
/**
 * chrome result
 *
 * useEffect in child
 * timeout in render
 */

/**
 * safari result
 *
 * timeout in render
 * useEffect in child
 */
```

## The expected behavior

The message should be same;

```jsx
/**
 * chrome result
 *
 * useEffect in child
 * timeout in render
 */

/**
 * safari result
 *
 * useEffect in child
 * timeout in render
 */
```

